subproject.corporate outcome: Strengthened national capacity for inclusive governance and coordination of national HIV responses, and for the protection of human rights of people affected by HIV, including women and other vulnerable groups
subproject.description: Strengthened national capacity for inclusive governance and coordination of AIDS responses and increased participation of civil society entities and people living with HIV in the design, implementation and evaluation of AIDS programmes; Policies and Programmes implemented through multi-stakeholder approaches to protect the human rights of people living with HIV, mitigate gender-related vulnerability and address the impact of AIDS on women and girls
subproject.gender code: Gender equality as a significant objective
subproject.title: RED RIBBON AWARD INITIATIVE
